<p><span style="font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif; font-size: 16px;"><strong><br />Hello {!Case.Contact},</strong></span></p>
<p><span style="font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif; font-size: 16px;">We&rsquo;re glad to hear from you!</span></p>
<p><span style="font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif; font-size: 16px;">There&rsquo;ve been some changes to the Honeywell customer ordering process since you were here last. Now, instead of emailing for order status updates, you&rsquo;ll log onto <a style="color: #c53223; font-weight: bold; text-decoration: none;" href="https://myaerospace.honeywell.com/" target="_blank">myaerospace.com</a>, and simply follow the prompts to check on your order.</span></p>
<p><span style="font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif; font-size: 16px;">It&rsquo;s important that you understand that in shifting to this new streamlined process Honeywell has completely disabled our email status update system. So please, log onto <a style="color: #c53223; font-weight: bold; text-decoration: none;" href="https://myaerospace.honeywell.com/" target="_blank">MyAerospace.com</a> to find the latest information on your order.</span></p>
<p><span style="font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif; font-size: 16px;">We appreciate you taking this one-time extra step. Rest assured, from now on out the portal will open a world of convenience, access, dependability, and speed for your company.</span></p>
